General.Name: Compagnie de Chemins de Fer Départementaux Société Anonyme
General.Description: Compagnie de Chemins de Fer Départementaux Société Anonyme engages in the provision of railway solutions in France. It offers railway equipment, including locomotives, shunters, railcars, funiculars, bogies, and railway gearboxes. The company was founded in 1881 and is headquartered in Paris, France.
